=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東京都自己去過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為成日買平機票唔洗同人夾<br />\n<br />\n雖然我個人本身都比較慢熱同內斂 簡單講即係毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得同唔熟唔太相處到既朋友去寧願自己去好似仲好"},{"pid":"046515ff97e9cb62b3b755f494f5bf7f8c3f7657","tid":179031,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:21:15.000Z","msg":"去上野公園"},{"pid":"928ef9487a9e07246bbf480a0dcf031417ad1714","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w3c9qt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w3c9qt.jpg&h=d1e6f068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實上年都去左睇櫻花 <br />\n呢張係上年係新宿御苑影既 個陣滿開 開始少少吹雪<br />\n今年去呢幾日好似天氣麻麻 同埋好似多數地方都未滿開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我諗欣賞下盛開中既櫻花都另有一番風味既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cc6636be065ae84608fa350324148afeaee89e","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去上野公園</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年去左 覺得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能個陣咁岩天氣麻麻地 有d 落雨 同埋又好多人<br />\n今年應該唔去上野公園<br />\n打算去氷川神社 千鳥ヶ淵 <br />\n有時間就可能去埋 六義園 代代木公園 <br />\n同上年都有去既目黑川"},{"pid":"5f5ac9971d081b94689a9e83b4576418f6d66b80","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPSMEKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPSMEKP.jpg&h=39b99c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成田出緊市區 就天黑了 差唔多就無左成日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊今晚食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99cda653bf142dde65eb58f1c8131f3eae91efa","tid":179031,"uid":3604