faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d37f0e37ba757d0696dbe41d8571b78cd126b4","tid":179031,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下樓主你覺得果邊體感溫度係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋想知公園多唔多人 （旅客多定本地人多）<br />\n<br />\n有冇學生妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定放曬假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗨"},{"pid":"b36a1d1508dd9f88858f162c1b2ed07e45310a20","tid":179031,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2b41dcbe4487eb3e014d4afad54c4cbdd98f7d","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下樓主你覺得果邊體感溫度係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋想知公園多唔多人 （旅客多定本地人多）<br />\n<br />\n有冇學生妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定放曬假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思岩岩番香港有d 忙而家先得閒覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東京個邊要睇下有冇太陽好唔好天<br />\n同一個溫度但有太陽同落雨我自己覺得體感溫度爭成10度<br />\n一落雨真係凍到hihi 有太陽就溫暖好多<br />\n公園多唔多人要睇下你去邊d 如果市匿出夠個d 應該點都多人<br />\n旅客同日本人都多 我就其中一日去左近郊<br />\n近郊就覺得日本人比較多 同埋個日係星期日<br />\n日本人都放假 平日就可能會比較少人<br />\n學生妹都有見到下 但無特別留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無記錯好似星期六日都見到著住校服既日本女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5473e12508d8ab7fdbb3dbde76057dfccef696","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockqu