d":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會食燒肉 有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我戒左豬肉 牛肉幾年 所以無食燒肉啊<br />\n但想搵咩好食可以去日版openrice 睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Fen%2F&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1f04cd00\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/en/</a><br />\n我個幾日都係靠依個搵野食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2a60fc460a8da9dbaf04946e7a30b575e86c52","tid":179031,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"六日都有學生妹出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddc3568560ac52c9c4127ad23eee8081fc4df5f","tid":179031,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e3af0e9ada6099d07848d74816da288a9afe78","tid":179031,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"巴打仲有無更新"},{"pid":"a8c2ce3c9f5a1cb63ec02fe2af5089e5d9f94a6b","tid":179031,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b26ab27454b01f8bcd6ebdc6595ea6831bd5008","tid":179031,"uid":36047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"一早番左香港喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁放假得閒睇番相機影既相<br />\n雖然係垃圾dc 仔但好似都係靚d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QU3R4z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/